{"tid":251042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋民直擊】幫人教仔惹禍？ 茶客被茶壺扑穿頭","createTime":"2017-05-20T14:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T09:10:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11d8d1770e61e83ff2e808f36a8f07f16edc31da","tid":251042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"【17：16更新】新增動新聞<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170520/large/1495259611_d1ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170520%2Flarge%2F1495259611_d1ed.jpg&h=10b0ae25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n土瓜灣有酒樓茶客爆茶壺傷人，嚇震全場！事發於土瓜灣馬頭圍道209號囍慶酒家，下午1時許，讀者周小姐偕母親到來飲茶，準備點菜之際，毗鄰傳來吵鬧聲，一名身材高大的中年漢情緒激動，喝罵同枱另一名六旬漢，批評對方「教壞」自己的兒子，未幾更拿起桌上的茶壺扑向對方前額。傷者登時頭破血流。周小姐說：「好得人驚呀，啲玻璃濺過嚟，到處都係。」<br />\n周小姐和在場其他食客被此場景嚇壞，部份人站起來，清理身上的玻璃碎片，「好多枱都嚇到走咗，我哋都驚到落去茶餐廳度食。」周小姐續稱，逞兇的男子繼續爆粗破口大罵，被在場兩名經理拉到一旁。而傷者滿面鮮血，「佢好冷靜，冇反抗，同枱另一名男子又冇乜理。」<br />\n警方稱，傷者姓嚴﹝63歲﹞與涉嫌傷人的黃姓男子﹝51歲﹞為舊同事，他們就金錢及教仔問題爭執，其間有人用茶壺襲擊對方。黃涉嫌襲擊傷人被捕，傷者則送院治理，案件由九龍城警區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170520/56718940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170520%2F56718940&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=f42a6e39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170520%2F56718940&h=a72ce9ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170520/56718940</a>"},{"pid":"4c52f3e16c80c4132dd5f20a2c9ad2f42804b628","tid":251042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T01:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb667b091e4748d2d6ebd5eb3451fc972f57afc","tid":251042,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ed1e8c32125766346ca07409794532069507db","tid":251042,"uid":39693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81403f1816f07f41f3483b833a588a7fde575201","tid":251042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6fb96a7ecf49edc1e6de98ec0b75bf433a1fe9","tid":251042,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"171cb82c0503e7e6d046933e47863373be7f0b54","tid":251042,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:10:39.000Z","msg":"班廢老有冇畀錢先走"}]}